column5: Would love to hear how you guys catch those Walleye in the summer. We have never fished Walleye before. We are going to Lac Seul July16/23 and would like to hear how we might catch some Walleye. We will be fishing in the Chamberlin Narrows area. Types of Rod /Reel & line Lures How to catch them Thank You, Glenn
Ultralight + jighead + minnow/worm + structure (point, hump, etc) = walleye + pike
